<h2 id="停止-v2raya-服务">停止 V2raya 服务</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"><span class="line"><span class="ln">1</span><span class="cl">sudo systemctl stop v2raya
</span></span></code></pre></div>

<h2 id="重置-v2raya-密码">重置 V2raya 密码</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"><span class="line"><span class="ln">1</span><span class="cl">sudo v2raya --reset-password
</span></span></code></pre></div><details open>
 <summary>Output</summary>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="ln">1</span><span class="cl">Config directory: /etc/v2raya
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="ln">2</span><span class="cl">Resetting password...
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="ln">3</span><span class="cl">If no response for a long time, please stop other v2rayA instances and try again.
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="ln">4</span><span class="cl">Succeed. It will work after you restart v2rayA.
</span></span></code></pre></div></details>


